d set an Olympic record low score in the dressage on Saturday to propel the reigning champions straight to the stop of the standings.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\", \"score\": 0.9999995741596647, \"rank\": 4.258404147590321e-07, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Austen\"}, {\"begin\": 2767, \"end\": 2775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stirling\", \"score\": 0.9999575928179109, \"rank\": 4.2408690943075145e-05, \"text\": \"Stirling\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stirling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stirling\"}, {\"begin\": 2966, \"end\": 2973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.915515369526277, \"rank\": 0.09228061893713939, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"William\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2737}, {\"ngram\": \"their hand\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"The best destinations\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"activities\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"the frontrunners\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"Collett\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"her horse\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"London\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic record low score\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3074}, {\"ngram\": \"the dres